       &lt;&gt;           An Exploration of The Quisling Syndrome          &lt;&gt;
       &lt;&gt;                             and                            &lt;&gt;
       &lt;&gt;  A Look At The Insurrection Of Security Into The Community &lt;&gt;
       &lt;&gt;                                                            &lt;&gt;
